## ServiceNow Integration
ServiceNow REST API
Pull data:
incident table
sys_audit
sys_journal_field
cmdb_ci
Python integration:
requests
httpx
pysnow (optional)

## Confluence Integration
Confluence Cloud REST API
creating postmortem pages
updating drafts
linking incidents

Example endpoint --> POST /wiki/rest/api/content
Python tools:
atlassian-python-api
or
requests

## Task Queue / Background Execution
 --> Incident analysis should run async.
 --> Celery OR simpler if GCP


## Google Cloud Tasks
Tasks handled:
extract incident
analyze timeline
generate RCA
publish page

## Data Storage

Ingestion Process:
pipeline runs
timeline events
scoring results
LLM outputs

PostgreSQL: Recommended tables

incident_pipeline_runs
incident_events
timeline_events
quality_scores
llm_outputs

